import React, { Component, Fragment} from 'react'

import Paper from '@material-ui/core/Paper'

import IconButton from '@material-ui/core/IconButton'
import SvgIcon from '@material-ui/core/SvgIcon'
import MyLocationIcon from '@material-ui/icons/MyLocation'
import SearchIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Search'
import AddLocationIcon from '@material-ui/icons/AddLocation'

import logo from "../public/logo.svg"

class actionsBar extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Paper elevation={3} style={{position: 'fixed', bottom:"10%", left:"5%", background:"white", display:"flex", flexDirection: "column", paddingBottom:"0%", paddingTop:"5%", borderRadius: "50px"}}>
        <IconButton aria-label="delete">
          <MyLocationIcon fontSize="large" />
        </IconButton>
        <IconButton aria-label="delete">
          <SearchIcon fontSize="large" />
        </IconButton>
        <IconButton aria-label="delete">
          <AddLocationIcon fontSize="large" />
        </IconButton>
        <Paper elevation={3}><SvgIcon color="secondary" component={logo} style={{borderRadius: "50%", width:'59px', height:"59px"}}></SvgIcon></Paper>
      </Paper>
    );
  }
}

export default actionsBar;
